1236
00:48:54,932 --> 00:48:55,975
Whoo-hoo!

1237
00:48:56,059 --> 00:48:58,144
Saya sangat gembira, saya boleh menangis.

1238
00:48:58,227 --> 00:48:59,854
Ayuh, Gerald. Biar saya lihat.

1239
